User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable Show

Entry
    title Text
    content Markdown
    posted UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIMESTAMP

Image
    filename Text
    description Textarea Maybe
    date UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
    deriving Show

